 * @section purpose Purpose
 *
 * kblog provides client-side support for weblogs.
 *
 * @section desc Description
 *
 * KBlog is a small library for access to Blogger 1.0, MetaWeblog, MovableType
 * and GData compatible blogs. It makes heavy use of the KXmlRpc client
